item.title: Unable to download cache HELP
item.dc:creator: @sk8rdude461 sk8rdude461
item.description:
@sk8rdude461 wrote:

The error is because it cannot download the cache for your client.

If you created the zip, make sure it’s zipped correctly.
If you didn’t, make sure the file exists and can be downloaded.

We also do not allow payment here, as help is free.
